tool_description: The most cheapest api that provides high quality crypto data.
title: Crypto Ranking Data

api_list.name: Last days fng
api_list.description:
Gives last number of days that you entered in limit parameter.
**for example last 7 days**
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://crypto-ranking-data.p.rapidapi.com/fng/{limit}"

headers = {
    "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
    "X-RapidAPI-Host": "crypto-ranking-data.p.rapidapi.com"
}

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)

print(response.json())

api_list.name: Crypto listing
api_list.description:
